flowchart LR
  U[User Request] --> P[Planner (LLM)\nproduces Plan JSON]
  P -->|proposed plan| X[Executor (Deterministic)\nschema + policy validation]
  X -->|validated tool call| T[Tool Adapter]
  T --> S[External Service/API]
  S --> T --> X
  X --> R[Final Response]
  X -->|reject + reason| E[Error/Repair Prompt\nto Planner]
  E --> P
